ENRICHED BLEACHED FLOUR (BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, NIACIN, IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), SUGAR, PARTIALLY HYDROGENATED SOYBEAN OIL WITH EMULSIFIER (SOY LECITHIN, MONO- AND DIGLYCERIDES), CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF: SODIUM BICARBONATE, SALT, EGG WHITES, DEFATTED SOY FLOUR, DEXTROSE, SODIUM ALUMINUM PHOSPHATE, MONOCALCIUM PHOSPHATE, BUTTERMILK SOLIDS, NONFAT MILK, TRICALCIUM PHOSPHATE, WHEY SOLIDS, ALUMINUM SULFATE, XANTHAN GUM.
